, bro..\"}]}","author":{"profile":"https://brilliant.org/profile/sajjad-toao2d/","name":"Sajjad Sajjad"},"date":"- 6 years, 2 months ago"}]},{"author":{"avatar":"../../brioche/avatars-2/resized/45/2faaf98f39ce0d178d98c5856196d40c.2faaf98f39ce0d178d98c5856196d40c.jpg?width=45","profile":"https://brilliant.org/profile/rama-vh1pbo/","name":"Rama Devi"},"date":"May 13, 2015, 11:10 p.m.","body":"{\"type\":\"doc\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"\\n                                \\n                                \\n                                \\n                                    \\n                                        \"},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Let the original number be 'a'\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"\\n\\n\"},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Let the divisor be 'd'\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"\\n\\n\"},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Let the quotient of the division of a by d be 'x'\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"\\n\\n\"},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Therefore, we can write the relation as a by d = x and the remainder is 24.\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"\\n\\n\"},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"i.e., a = dx + 24\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"\\n\\n\"},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"When twice the original number is divided by d, 2a is divided by d.\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"\\n\\n\"},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"We know that a = dx + 24. Therefore, 2a = 2dx + 48\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"\\n\\n\"},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The problem states that 2dx + 48 by d leaves a remainder of 11.\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"\\n\\n\"},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"2dx is per